<h2><a class="listing" style="document" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/Supporting-international-cooperation-in-environmental-nanotechnology" title="Supporting international cooperation in environmental nanotechnology" alt="document">Supporting international cooperation in environmental nanotechnology</a></h2>

	
	
	
	
					<p>The ICPC-NanoNet project can support international research cooperation in environmental nanotechnology between the European Union and International Cooperation Partner Countries to the EU (emerging economies and developing countries). This article focuses on the case of nanotechnology for water purification. The article can be found online <a href="http://www.nano.org.uk/articles/35/" target="_blank">here</a> </p>
							<p><span class="date">23/02/2010</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="document" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/Supporting-international-cooperation-in-environmental-nanotechnology">Read more...</a>
