						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/Nuance-newsletter-UbuntuNet-Alliance-Vol-2-Issue-9-January-2010" title="Nuance newsletter - UbuntuNet Alliance - Vol 2: Issue 9: January 2010" alt="link">Nuance newsletter - UbuntuNet Alliance - Vol 2: Issue 9: January 2010</a></h2>

	
					<p>NUANCE is a monthly e-newsletter published by UbuntuNet Alliance. Key content is news from, about, or of interest to National Research and Education Networks (NRENs) in Africa.</p>
							<p><span class="date">4/02/2010</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
